column2: SELECT TOP #   s.ra, s.dec,       s.z, s.zErr,   log1#(s.velDisp) as logsigstar, log1#(e) * s.velDispErr / s.velDisp as logsigstarErr,   s.snMedian,      l.Sigma_Ha_#, l.Sigma_Ha_#_Err,   log1#(l.Sigma_Hb_#) as logsigB, l.Sigma_Hb_#_Err/l.Sigma_Hb_# as logsigBErr,      mpa.lgm_tot_p5# as lgm, (mpa.lgm_tot_p8#-mpa.lgm_tot_p1#)/#. as lgm_Err,   mpa.sfr_tot_p5# as lsfr, (mpa.sfr_tot_p8#-mpa.sfr_tot_p1#)/#. as lsfr_Err    INTO mydb.methclass FROM SpecObj AS s   JOIN emissionLinesPort as l ON s.specobjid=l.specobjid JOIN galSpecExtra as mpa on s.specobjid=mpa.specobjid
